    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an immaculate 2017 Shelby GT350, a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the 5.2L 'Voodoo' V8 with its distinctive flat-plane crankshaft, delivering 526 hp and an 8,250 RPM redline through a precise Tremec TR-3160 six-speed manual. The chassis is equipped with MagneRide active damping and a 3.73 Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit stability. This vehicle has been maintained to a concours standard, showing no signs of heat-cycling on the Brembo braking system or aerodynamic wear. The engine bay is detailed to factory specifications, and the undercarriage remains spotless, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance.",
